## 04 — Title Screening

Populated by `/screen --stage title` as an accretive log. The first run writes `### iter-0 (initial classification)` combining the pass-1 (regex) and pass-2 (LLM) records. Refinements via `/screen --refine` append `### iter-K (after refine: <summary>)` blocks. Lock time appends `### final` with the user's verdict and a pointer at `locked_at_iteration`.

### iter-0 (initial classification)

- **regex_decision:** `<Include | Exclude>`
- **regex_justification:** `"<verbatim PT-BR string from the winning category>"`
- **winning_category:** `<category_id | default>`
- **overrides_applied:** `[<override_id>, …]`
- **evidence_trail:**
  - `{ category: <category_id>, pattern_id: <pattern_id>, matched_substring: "<substring>", position: [<start>, <end>] }`
  - `{ … }`
- **llm_decision:** `<Include | Exclude>`
- **llm_justification:** `"<1–3 sentences PT-BR>"`
- **agrees_with_regex:** `<true | false>`
- **divergence_reason:** `<null | "<1–2 sentences PT-BR citing evidence_trail or a missed signal>">`
- **model:** `<model id used at pass 2>`
- **timestamp:** `<ISO timestamp>`

### final

- **my_final_decision:** `<Include | Exclude>`
- **my_justification:** `"<free text from the spreadsheet's My Justification cell>"`
- **locked_at_iteration:** `<iter-K>` (the iteration whose verdict the user kept)
- **locked_at:** `<ISO timestamp of [04] lock>`

---

## 05 — Abstract Screening

Populated by `/screen --stage abstract`. Same accretive structure as stage 04, with input expanded to title + abstract + keywords. Patterns idle at stage 04 (`applicable_stages` excludes `title`) become active here when their reliability is higher on abstract evidence.

### iter-0 (initial classification)

- **regex_decision:** `<Include | Exclude>`
- **regex_justification:** `"<verbatim PT-BR string>"`
- **winning_category:** `<category_id | default>`
- **overrides_applied:** `[<override_id>, …]`
- **evidence_trail:**
  - `{ category: <category_id>, pattern_id: <pattern_id>, matched_substring: "<substring>", position: [<start>, <end>] }`
  - `{ … }`
- **llm_decision:** `<Include | Exclude>`
- **llm_justification:** `"<1–3 sentences PT-BR>"`
- **agrees_with_regex:** `<true | false>`
- **divergence_reason:** `<null | "<…>">`
- **model:** `<model id>`
- **timestamp:** `<ISO timestamp>`

### final

- **my_final_decision:** `<Include | Exclude>`
- **my_justification:** `"<free text>"`
- **locked_at_iteration:** `<iter-K>`
- **locked_at:** `<ISO timestamp of [05] lock>`

