## 07 — Taxonomy

Populated by `/07-taxonomy-development` across multiple iterations before `taxonomy-locked`, then finalized in the lock pass. Only present for papers with `06-full-text-screening: include`.

### 07a — Open coding

Free-form codes emitted per paper during iteration 1 and any subsequent re-coding triggered by criterion refinements.

- **Codes proposed in iteration `<k>`:**
  - `"<code phrase>"` — confidence `<LOW | MED | HIGH>` — evidence:
    > `<verbatim snippet>`
    - Location: `<section, page>`
  - `"<code phrase>"` — confidence `<…>` — evidence:
    > `<…>`
- **Checkpoint:** `<none | see stages/07-taxonomy-development.md#coding-checkpoint-paper-NNNN>`
- **Commit:** `<hash>`

### 07b — Final classification (post-lock)

One entry per axis declared in CLAUDE.md §8.1, with the chosen value and anchoring evidence.

- **axis `<axis-name>`:** `<value>` — confidence `<LOW | MED | HIGH>` — evidence:
  > `<verbatim snippet>`
  - Location: `<section, page>`
  - Reason: `<why this value, not the neighbors>`
- **Checkpoint:** `<none | see stages/07-taxonomy-development.md#classify-checkpoint-paper-NNNN>`
- **Commit:** `<hash>`

